Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則  這就是社會主義\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Otherwise, it was just socialism,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是注定要失敗的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}which is built to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗是不會為你加分的  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And you don't get points for failure, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們不想要失敗  他們要的是成功\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}People don't want failure. They want success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就討論一下最近的功績吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's discuss our recent success then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直指責總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You have been very critical of the president
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對恐怖活動的態度不夠強硬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for not being strong on terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在上周  特種部隊逮捕了尤瑟夫·艾哈邁迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Just last week, U.S. Special forces captured Yusuf Al Ahmadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把他收監入獄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and they have him in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你現在會不會說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So would you now say that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對總統的指責是毫無根據的呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}your criticism of the president was unfounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對艾哈邁迪的逮捕是一個進步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The capture of Ahmadi is a step forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正的問題是長久的安全\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but the real issue here is sustained security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統沒跟敘利亞人打招呼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president sent in American troops
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就派出了美國軍隊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}without consulting the Syrians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那對我們日后與他們的合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, that's gonna do real damage to our ability
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將造成很大傷害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to work with them in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點不在于建功立業\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}See, this isn't about notches in a belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是給我們國家以更安全的世界環境\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's about a safer world for our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我們的孩子一個更好的未來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}A better future for our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州長  我明白"安全""孩子"等字眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Governor, I understand that words like "safer"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很好的效果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and "children" play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但國家安全是一個復雜且千變萬化的領域\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But national security is a complex and ever-changing landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也需要約束\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that sometimes requires restraint,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也需要果斷的行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}sometimes decisive action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我覺得我們最好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So I think maybe we want to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下眼前聽起來不錯的詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}put aside what sounds good in the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實一點討論適合我們的政策\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and be adaptable with our policy in terms of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要人教我什么是現實\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I don't need a lecture on reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我還是小男生似的  安德伍德夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}like I'm a schoolboy, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正在中東打過仗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've actually fought in the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So has the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們對國際外交的觀點并不只是花言巧語\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our views on international diplomacy aren't just pretty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以如你所愿討論政策  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can debate policy all you'd like, Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一件事不容置疑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but there is one thing that is undebatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是沒有了領袖的哈里發國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And that is ICO is no longer the threat it once was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅性已不比從前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}without their leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不看辯論嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not watching the debate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他們要說什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know what they're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能幫你什么  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How can I help you, Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴過你會有這么一天的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told you there'd be a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全可以帶著這些光榮退休\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's no reason you shouldn't keep this and retire with honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How are we looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"千變萬化"很有沖擊力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, high impact on "ever-changing."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威上鉤了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And Conway took the bait
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連"小男生"和"花言巧語"都出來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and played right into "schoolboy" and "pretty",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合起來就是"可愛男生"  太美妙了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}which gives you "pretty boy." It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚姻的事怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What about the marriage stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們越是反復在任何語境中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, the more they can keep saying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說"一起"  "超越"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"together" and "beyond" and "become"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和"成為"  我們都加分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}in any context, we score on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會跟你討論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't discuss the private conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們情報委員會的私下談話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we have on the Intelligence Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告密會讓你孤立無援\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whistle-blowing insulates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給我黨提名人拆臺嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And kneecap my party's nominee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會在這次辯論中說謊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's going to lie about it at this debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They both are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是說出真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're going to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能二者兼得  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can't have it both ways, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們抓到他了  結束\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We got him, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是單方面  目光短淺的行為\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Unilateral, short-sighted action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單方面是因為你和將軍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Unilateral because you and the general
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓共和黨就跟俄羅斯人合作的事反對我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}pitted the Republicans against my involving the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是無稽之談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's just not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說你沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you saying that you did not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓將軍跟眾議院情報委員會的人聯系嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}have the general contact members of the House Intelligence Committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍  你愿意評論一下嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}General, would you care to comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我辭去職務后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When I resigned my commission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不再跟國會的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I stopped talking to members of Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談論國家安全事宜了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}about matters of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你是說你沒有嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So you are saying that you did not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  女士  我沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, ma'am. I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都知道你插手了  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You and I both know that you interfered, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我私下問你的時候  你都承認了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You admitted so much to me when I asked you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我說將軍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You told me that the general
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾跟委員會的成員談過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}had spoken to members of that committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你說的是我在委員會有朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told you that I have friends on the committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}which is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是我干涉了委員會的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not that I interfere with committee work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓每個共和黨人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You lined up every Republican
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都反對俄羅斯入局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to be opposed to the Russians being involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都一致反對了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was unanimous opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你打算放棄鉆井\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, if your plan was to get Russian support
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以獲得俄羅斯的支持  我不怪他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}by giving away drill sites, I don't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們明確一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So just to be absolutely clear, for the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州長  你是說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you are saying, Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本人或是將軍都沒有聯系過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that neither you nor the General made any contact
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾議院情報委員會的任何成員嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with any member of the House Intelligence Committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I absolutely did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是讓我左右為難\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're putting me in an impossible place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偽造服役記錄時就將自己置于這種境地了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You put yourself there when you lied about your service record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想曝光誰的謊言\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whose lie do you want exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威的還是你自己的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Conway's or yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家想一想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Go home and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用趕在明天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doesn't need to happen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在選舉日之前就行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It just needs to happen before Election Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想抹煞你對于你丈夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not trying to diminish your contribution
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統工作的貢獻  安德伍德夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to your husband's presidency, Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我對你的經驗表示質疑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I do question your experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人在當上總統時\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No one's fully prepared to be President
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就充分準備好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}when he or she becomes one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看民調結果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And look at the polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全國支持第一夫人做副總統的選民過半\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Over half the country is open to a First Lady as VP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要一位新總統的選民也過半\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And more than half of the country wants a new president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確實在民調中暫時領先  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's true that you are leading in the polls for now, Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但近幾周內  差距正在縮小\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but the gap has been closing in recent weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當人們前去投票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, when people show up to vote
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不面對克萊爾·安德伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and have to confront the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為總統的可能性\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}of Claire Underwood as President,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就要摸摸良心  做出正確的選擇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}they're gonna have a gut check and make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得非常對  那意味著他們會投給我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're absolutely right. That means they'll vote for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們想想就會發現\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because they'll look around and realize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我出了什么事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that if anything happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們能放心讓克萊爾接手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}they'll be in very good hands with Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她說得對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And, you know, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人能在做總統前完全準備好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No one can prepare to become the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我已經是總統了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I have been the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我知道那需要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and now I know what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要的是信心  坦誠和效力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It requires confidence, openness, effectiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而克萊爾具備所有這些品質\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and Claire has all of those qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry, Mr. President. It...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎我們得暫停一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It looks like we have to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稍后將繼續進行史上首次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll return shortly to the first-ever simultaneous debate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統候選人和競選搭檔的同場辯論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}between presidential candidates and their running mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已停\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  安德伍德夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President, Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位請跟我來一下好嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}would you please come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們是美國公民\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"We are citizens of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們被哈里發帝國組織  以真主之名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have been taken hostage in the name of God
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為人質扣押"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}by the Islamic Caliphate Organization."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們國家犯下了非法侵略\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"Our country is guilty of illegal aggression
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大規模屠殺穆斯林的罪行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and mass murder against Muslims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們懇求寬恕"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We beg for mercy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有滿足以下要求  哈里發國才會給予寬恕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}ICO will grant mercy only if these demands are met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  停止美軍在敘利亞的一切軍事行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}One, cessation of all U.S. Military activity in Syria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二  向哈里發支付一百億美元賠償\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Two, ten billion dollars in reparations paid to the Caliphate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三  安全送還我們遭到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Three, the safe return of our leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不公正囚禁的領導人  尤瑟夫·艾哈邁迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yusuf Al Ahmadi, from his unjust imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會和罪犯弗蘭克·安德伍德溝通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We will not communicate with the criminal Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只和他的繼任者威廉·康威溝通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We will only communicate with his successor, William Conway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如未能在24小時內滿足以上要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If these demands aren't met in 24 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將不予以寬恕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}mercy will not be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視頻在七個渠道上發布\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Released to seven outlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過加密郵件和暗網\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Encrypted email, Deep Web.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三名人質是吉姆和卡洛琳·米勒夫婦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The hostages are Jim and Caroline Miller,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和女兒梅莉莎  是諾克斯維爾人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}their daughter Melissa, from Knoxville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  不論你需要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President, whatever you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意提供幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm here to offer assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會告知你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們目前識別出了板墻和照明設備\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So far, we've identified the drywall and lighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是美國制造的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All U.S. Manufactured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視頻是用松下高清攝影機錄制\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The video was shot on a Panasonic HD camcorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美國銷量最大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}most widely sold in the States.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以確定他們在國內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So we know they're in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民航班機可以排除\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, commercial flight is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人飛機不太可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Private plane is unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們很肯定他們是乘坐陸地交通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're confident that they traveled by ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是米勒家被劫持的汽車\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}probably the Millers' hijacked car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后已知地點是諾克斯維爾市外一家丹尼餐廳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Last known location is a Denny's just outside of Knoxville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一筆借記卡交易\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}A debit card transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他們離開餐廳的影像\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is footage of them leaving the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們心系米勒一家人及其親友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our hearts go out to the Millers' family and loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們相信總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But we're confident that the President
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在盡一切可能營救他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}is doing everything possible to achieve their release.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴總統  我們愿意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told the President that we'd be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供任何協助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to assist in any way if it would be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時此刻美國必須團結一致并...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is a time when America needs to pull together and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是"團結一致并為米勒一家人祈禱"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's "pull together and pray for the Millers."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后再換我...  -我沒忘詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- And then I come in, and-- - I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是認為這樣做不對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just feel this is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此舉暗示我們愿意與恐怖分子談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It implies we're willing to negotiate with terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該保持沉默\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We should keep our mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓當權者去做他們的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let the authorities do their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持沉默不會為我們獲得新聞版面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't get press by keeping our mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經讓我在全國節目上說謊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You had me lie on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還要我們發布這種\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And now you want us to send out some video
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會刺激恐怖分子的視頻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that only encourages these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這么做只為博得版面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And you wanna do that to score some press coverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你認為這么做不妥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If it doesn't make you feel comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以自己來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在外面等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've had enough of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說的確實有道理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論我們是否發布這視頻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Look, they're gonna kill that family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都會殺害那一家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}whether we send this out or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還不如說我愿意盡義務出面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We might as well say I was willing to show up for duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須說  我同意將軍的看法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I have to say, I agree with the General.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始錄像\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Press record.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始錄像\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Press record!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們心系米勒一家人及其親友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our hearts go out to the Millers' family and loved ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于劫持者我們掌握了什么信息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do we know about the captor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們敘利亞的線人說這是起單獨行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our Syrian assets say this is a lone wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上  是兩人的行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Two wolves, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們調高了視頻的對比度后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When we pumped up the contrast in the video,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在墻上發現了一個從攝影機后投射出的人影\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we saw a shadow on the wall from someone behind the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,語音分析認為歹徒來自田納西州西孟菲斯地區\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Voice analysis points to western Tennessee, Memphis area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  我能說幾句嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, Mr. President, if I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍爾布魯克探員  我們的頂尖談判專家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Agent Holbrooke, our top negotiating expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們針對這種事件進行過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, we've run 16 possible models in preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16種情況模擬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for an incident like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的事件包含三種情況的關鍵因素\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, what we have here are key elements from three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國綁架犯  兒童遭綁架\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}American kidnappers, the abduction of a child
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及要求溝通代理人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and proxy communication...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為什么指名康威\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why did they want Conway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是重點  我告訴你為什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's the real question. I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為換做是我  我也會這么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because I would've done exactly the same thing if it had been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能削弱我的權威\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It undermines my authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我措手不及  挑起對立\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Throws me off balance. Pits me against my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還因為我沒有孩子  而康威有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And because I don't have children, and he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們知道我不會妥協\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They know I won't compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有總統會妥協\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No president would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但康威這樣的總統候選人  或許會妥協\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But a would-be president like Conway, well, he might.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰術上我們需要更多時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tactically, we need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法保證我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't guarantee that we can
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24小時內能追蹤到他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}track them down in less than 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  我的計劃是這樣的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Enough. Here's what I wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統正與聯調局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president is working with the FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及其他執法和情報部門合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and other law enforcement and intelligence agencies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找米勒一家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to locate the Millers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了確保這些行動不受干擾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, in order to protect the integrity of those efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我目前無法透露任何行動的具體進展\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I won't be sharing any details on their progress at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時  總統還尋求康威州長的支援\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}In the meantime, the president is reaching out to Governor Conway
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為一旦與劫持者建立了聯系作準備\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}should contact with the captors be established.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一點我要說清\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, let me be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這并不是談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're not talking about negotiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是溝通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}just communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大可先私下問我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You could've asked me privately first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是戰略  向劫持者顯示\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was tactical, to show the kidnappers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們尊重他們的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that we respect their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我別無選擇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This doesn't leave me a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拒絕嘛  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, you can always say no, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已有一份計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have a plan for how we can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使沒有你的參與也能處理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}handle this without your participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么進行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How would that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會公開表示\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I say publicly that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意親自與劫持者談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm willing to speak to the captors myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們拒絕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, if they refuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得做最壞的打算\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we'd have to be prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們團隊相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But our team believes that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在  我們建立對話的機會比較大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you give us a better shot at opening a dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好為我們爭取時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To buy us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你答應\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And if you do say yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們希望你盡快到白宮來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we'd want you at the White House as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要和我的團隊討論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I need to discuss with my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你會同意協助我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm hoping that you'll agree to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何  我盡快需要答復\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Either way, I'll need an answer soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解  一小時內會給你回復\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I understand. I'll let you know within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都有缺點  而這就是康威的缺點\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Everyone has a flaw, and this is Conway's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和總統談過  我說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I spoke with the president, and I said that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿提供任何協助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm willing to assist in any way if it would be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他渴望聚光燈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He aches for the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則他幾乎感覺自己是隱形的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He feels almost invisible without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他在這個舞臺的中央\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, if he's center stage on this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不能挑我的刺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he can't fault my performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們要共享這個舞臺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because we're sharing the stage together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被喝倒彩  他就也被喝倒彩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I get booed, he gets booed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但康威渴望的其實是掌聲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But it's really the applause that Conway's hungry for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  他會同意的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Trust me, he'll say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞臺太大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The stage is too big
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈光太過誘人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and the spotlight too tempting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他受不了...僅僅當一個觀眾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for him to be... a mere spectator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已經公開聲明如果他需要我會協助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I've already said publicly I'd assist if he asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是個錯誤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That was a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該更努力阻止的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I should've pushed back on it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不能讓他利用你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But you can't let him take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說都說了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I've said it. It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們得往前走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And now we have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這玩意真難喝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is fucking disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說  "經過慎重考慮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You say, "After much consideration,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不愿意與恐怖分子談判"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't feel comfortable negotiating with terrorists."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不僅成了一個騙子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And then I come off not only as a liar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是個懦夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but as a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都領先了  為什么要這么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why do this when we're ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領先多少  5個百分點  那不是領先\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}By what? Five points? That's not a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是碰運氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's a coin toss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整場競選我傳達的信息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My message this entire campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為國家服務  承擔責任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}has been about serving the country, showing up for duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在三軍統帥要我幫忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and now I'm gonna not show up when the Commander-in-Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻拒絕嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}has asked for my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...語言模式\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...and the speech patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫持者是視頻中說話的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The captor is the one who you heard on the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是美國人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Seems to be American.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從他公布視頻的方式可以看出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And the way he's released the video shows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個電腦行家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he's computer savvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里發國招募人員已轉向使用社交網絡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, ICO recruiters have been turning to social media networks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如臉書  推特  圖片分享\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}like Facebook, Twitter, Instagram,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些認同支持他們事業的用戶取得聯系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to initiate contact with users sympathetic to their cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-湯姆  -之前的組織  如基地組織\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Oh, Tom. - Earlier groups, like al-Qaeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用社交網絡的程度\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}didn't use social networking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,均遠遠不及哈里發國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}anywhere near the degree that ICO has.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫持者有可能...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It is possible that this captor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -飛行順利嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mr. President. - Good flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有點顛簸  不過還好  -進來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- A little bumpy, but fine. - Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你彈嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個有待爭論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, that's debatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我確實收集\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I definitely collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個大事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, this is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  太可怕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, it's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不羨慕此刻的弗蘭克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't envy Frank right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喝咖啡還是茶  -不用了  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Coffee? Tea? - No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了這么多事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I appreciate you taking the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激你愿騰出時間見我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}given everything that's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正又沒人打電話尋求我的建議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's not as though anyone's calling for my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這篇文章目前似乎沒那么重要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Although I'm not sure this article is pertinent at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是來談你的獎學基金的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not here about your scholarship fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白了  我的助理說你想寫...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't understand. My assistant said you wanted to write--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒謊了...好讓你肯見我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I lied... so you'd meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有國內監控項目  處于調試階段\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have a domestic surveillance program, beta phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是找出哈里發國招募的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}aimed at finding ICO recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外國情報監視法法庭裁決下來時我聽到了匯報\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was briefed when we got the FISA court ruling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是國內調查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, this is a domestic investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須通過聯調局工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have to work through the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們準備派出一支隊伍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, they're sending over a team,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望國土安全部和中情局加入\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I'd like for Homeland and the CIA to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事很敏感  你不應該關起門辦事嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is a sensitive program. Shouldn't you keep it in-house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們過去曾因不讓別的機構加入而受批評\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've been criticized for not involving other agencies in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想避免這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想要安全許可  -越快越好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You want clearances? - As soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情緊急  需要齊心協力  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's all hands on deck, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-州長  -總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Governor. - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位一定是查理了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, and this must be Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-查理...  -和總統握手  查理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Charlie... - Shake the President's hand, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-來呀  查理  -你說他是個吸血鬼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Come on, Charlie. - You said he was a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  你在這兒很安全\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, don't worry. You're safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮里沒有妖怪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No monsters in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶你們去住的地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll show you where you're staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  走吧  查理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay. Come on, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去過總統辦公室嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have you ever been in the Oval?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候去過一次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Once, when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,童子軍  我們見了里根\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My Boy Scout troop, we met with Reagan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你們會想住在一起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I thought you'd all like to be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以安排在了這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so I've put you in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想  我們可以讓孩子住林肯臥室\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but, if not, we can put the kids in the Lincoln Bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  這兒太棒了  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, this is wonderful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以后就要住這里嗎  媽媽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is this where we're gonna live, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那得看大選的結果了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll have to see how the election goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有股臭味兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Something smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  莉莉需要換尿布了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, gosh. Lily needs a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問哪里有...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Um, where--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這兒往右走就是衛生間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The restroom is here, to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我把一個共和黨人送進白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You want me to put a Republican in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想要一個共和黨  還是一個罪犯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You want a Republican or a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對黨還是忠誠的  湯姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I still have loyalty to my party, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他們對你的忠誠呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And where's their loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都打算彈劾你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They were going to impeach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰姬·夏普說服了民主黨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Jackie Sharp whipped Democrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的國務卿也背棄了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your own Secretary of State turned her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的黨  已經爛到核心了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your party? It's rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那個核心  就是安德伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And the core is Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷了你的總統之位你就不生氣嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Aren't you angry that he stole your presidency?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然生氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我氣我自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm angry at myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能料到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for not seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還氣我沒和他斗到底\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And for not fighting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就現在反擊吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So do something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來想說塔斯克撒謊了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wanted to say Tusk lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得到特赦后  我知道沒人會相信我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But once I got the pardon, I knew nobody would believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"消失吧  躲得遠遠的"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"Just disappear. Go away."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那種憤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And that anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我退隱了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I went away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股怒氣也會消失\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that anger would go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相要曝光了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The truth is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來揭露吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Be part of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民眾會相信你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}People will believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等媒體發布會一結束  你的任務就完成了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Once we finish with the press conference, you'll be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面交給我們就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們聯系我們  你不需要我接電話嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't want me on the call if they contact us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任務只是把他們引出來  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, you're only there for bait, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓你代表白宮和他們談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't have you speaking on behalf of the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說了想和我交涉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They said they wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  但我們有計劃了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, we have a roadmap in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就調整一下吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then you'll have to adjust it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么資格大搖大擺走進來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What right do you have to walk in here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們的應對方案指手畫腳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and dictate how we're gonna handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來也是擔了風險的  這你知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I put myself on the line coming here, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大可撒手不管  讓你自己焦頭爛額去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I could've backed off and left this pile of shit in your lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我要和你一起出鏡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, if I'm gonna be exposed with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我對談判方案就得有發言權\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}then I'm gonna have some say in how that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我就回紐約  看著你出丑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Or I head back to New York and watch you squirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中我下懷\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Just as I'd hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他攙和得越深越好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The more involved, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請接格林處長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Director Green, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們來了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-來了  -多謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- They're here. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們局長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is our director.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好  -這是總統幕僚長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Hello. - President's Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要過去三天內所有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need every white male under 40
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動范圍不正常的40歲以下白人男性的資料\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with geo-local anomalies in the past 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已整理好了  也和你們的監視名單核對過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Already done that, cross-referenced with your watchlists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在匹配電話語音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're voice matching with phone calls now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會派一支隊伍進駐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, we're bringing a team in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局  中情局  國安部和我們的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}FBI, CIA, Homeland, along with our own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時參與的人太多只會...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, yeah, more cooks in the kitchen won't--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經給他們權限了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've cleared them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能在溝通上耽誤時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can't waste time grapevining this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家坐在一起工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's get everyone working from the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要組織工作流程\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to organize workflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我們去我辦公室談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Right. Uh, let's talk in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往右第二間就是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's the second door on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有問題嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is this going to be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更希望他們不要監視我工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd prefer them not breathing down my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問的不是這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That wasn't my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了  都掩蓋好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told you, we're masked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  請坐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you. Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想感謝康威州長同意來協助我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to thank Governor Conway for agreeing to assist us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我的目標是一致的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He and I share the same goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是讓米勒一家安全回家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}which is the safe return of the Millers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為實現這一目的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}In order to achieve that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將和劫持者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we're willing to open up lines
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過專線進行交涉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}of communication with their captors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將作為你和總統之間的調解人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will act as intermediary between you and the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和我們聯系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To communicate with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需依次撥打吉姆和卡洛琳·米勒的社保號\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}dial Jim Miller's social security number followed by Caroline's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用任何手機或網絡運營商都可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}into any phone or Internet conferencing service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后將會有語音識別提示\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There will be a voice recognition prompt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓米勒一家念出自己的名字和即時時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have all three Millers say their names and state the time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連線即會建立\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and that will connect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們心系米勒一家和他們的親屬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our hearts are with the Millers and their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚和他們的親人通了話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I spoke to their siblings and their parents last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還在堅持著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and they remain strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呼吁全體國民  為了他們  保持堅強\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And I would ask all Americans to remain strong on their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然眼下情勢非常險惡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Deplorable as this situation is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們不能怪罪全體伊斯蘭人士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we cannot blame Islam as a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不應牽連國內渴望和平的數百萬穆斯林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or the millions of Muslims in our nation who yearn for peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為我們的社會辛勤奉獻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who contribute to our society,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和所有美國人共享一個美國夢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who have the same dreams as all Americans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里發國不能代表伊斯蘭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}ICO does not represent Islam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是某些別有用心的人會利用這次事件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But there are those who would use this incident
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為采取強硬措施尋找借口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to justify draconian measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如出行限制或強制注冊等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}like travel restrictions or forced registration,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這是在鼓吹仇恨  甚至暴力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who would espouse hatred or even violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦愛國走上了偏執的歧路\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The moment bigotry becomes a form of patriotism,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國就不再是美國了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}America is no longer America.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我今天來到國會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That is why I'm here today, in the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吁各位眾議員\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to urge our congressmen and women...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說有人支持籌贖金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hear there's a push to get the ten billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,財政委員會吵翻了天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Big debate in Ways and Means,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是絕對到不了眾議院表決\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but it'll never make it to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝裝樣子而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在和撥款委員會談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've been with Appropriations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-想繞過財政委嗎  -不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Bypass Ways and Means? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為向敘利亞派地面部隊增兵作撥款準備\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To pay for more ground troops in Syria if we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什么約我來這里  而不是在國會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So why are you meeting me instead of at the Capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆·漢默施密特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tom Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也聯系你了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Has he called you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯系了  但我什么都沒說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He reached out, but I haven't said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃克公開聲明了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Walker went on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他是我發動本黨議員彈劾他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Told him I was the one who whipped the votes for impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的說辭就是你認為他有罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your story is you thought he was guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒什么不對的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說你和他談過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So you have talked to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有幾個推論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He has some theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是把他想錯的地方澄清了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All I did was shake my head at the parts that weren't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不開口  就不會擔責任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're clean if you don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想開口  接受他采訪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I want to. On the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你也該這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think you should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些照片一泄露  你的眾議員席位就不保了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You will lose your seat as soon as those photos are leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也快保不住了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I may lose my seat anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威的超級政治行動委員會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Conway's super PAC is targeting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:24:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在針對所有選情嚴峻的加州民主黨參選人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}every California Democrat in a tight race.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我贏了  國會也是共和黨占多數\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Even if I win, I'm in a Republican-controlled Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統也是共和黨人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with a Republican president...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就是再給安德伍德當四年走狗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or I have to do Underwood's bidding for the next four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艾倫呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What about Alan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我們的事告訴他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told him about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挺大度的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He was kind about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等事情消停了  我們就離婚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll divorce once everything quiets down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不希望照片流出  那我不開口就是了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you don't want the photos out there, I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎全世界怎么議論我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't care about what the rest of the world thinks of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.89,0:24:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想保護你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All I cared about was protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們站出來吧  雷米\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then let's do this, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們站出來  他就完了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You and I go on the record, he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.71,0:24:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書亞·馬斯特森  田州理工計算科學專業\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Joshua Masterson. Computer science major at Tennessee Tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.02,0:24:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去兩年一直熱衷于研究\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Taken a keen interest in Islamic studies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.13,0:24:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和伊斯蘭教有關的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}during the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.24,0:24:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連續翹課三天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hasn't been to class in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.83,0:25:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有與親友聯系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}None of his friends or family have heard from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.89,0:25:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的聲音和視頻里的匹配\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Voice matches the one in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們判斷他的同伙是扎克瑞·霍松\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We believe his associate is Zachary Hawthorne,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.10,0:25:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中輟學  和馬斯特森關系很近\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}high school dropout who's remained close with Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上周二開始翹班\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Stopped showing up for work last Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他們打來  我應該...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So if they call, should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.72,0:25:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要表明我們知道他們的身份嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}should I tell them that we know who they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.44,0:25:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你只要自我介紹就行  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, you'll introduce yourself, Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后介紹我來接手對話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}then you introduce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.17,0:25:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  讓州長和他們交涉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, the governor will do the talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底能不能用他們的名字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so should he use their names or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.13,0:25:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可能會刺激他們做出沖動之舉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It could cause them to do something rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.51,0:25:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪奇探員是我們的首席心理學家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Agent March, our head psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.65,0:25:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不能提\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但反過來說  這或許能使他們回歸常人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Conversely, it could humanize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消除匿名給他們的信心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Removes the confidence of anonymity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.26,0:25:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果他們因此逃跑  那就壞事了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But if they run, it compromises everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此  我們確信這就是他們的身份\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not just that. We're confident on the IDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是有極微小的可能猜錯了人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but if there's the slightest chance we're wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就會削弱我們在談判中的地位\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it weakens our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那電話里先別提他們的名字了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then don't use their names in the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.48,0:25:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我們的對話腳本\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, sir, our script is written
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.43,0:25:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以我作為交涉人撰寫的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with the understanding that I'd be speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.29,0:25:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還需要為州長重新調整\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'd have to rework it for the governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.15,0:25:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那馬上進行調整\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, then let's rework it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不知道他們什么時候會打來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't know when they'll be calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.28,0:25:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在的情況很糟糕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know, the circumstances are awful,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.27,0:25:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還是得承認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I have to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.93,0:26:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能從競選中解脫一小會兒真是太棒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it's been nice to take a break from the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么做到的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't know how you do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時當競選搭檔和第一夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}running mate and First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.38,0:26:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上我自己也在琢磨呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm still trying to figure that out myself, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.82,0:26:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這令人敬佩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think it's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.16,0:26:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們贏了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If we win,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.94,0:26:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做點更新圖片分享之外的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd love to do something more than update my Instagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.59,0:26:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時批評那個  只是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When I criticized that, it was just because--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.45,0:26:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒關系  我不介意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, not at all. I didn't take offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.20,0:26:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是政治\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.30,0:26:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做點類似你槍支法案那樣的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd love to do something like your gun bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.40,0:26:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能通過參議院真是遺憾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a shame it didn't pass the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.91,0:26:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你支持那項立法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You support that legislation?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來自英格蘭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mmm, I'm from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.25,0:26:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們認為你們對槍支的癡迷太瘋狂了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We think your gun obsession is madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾也是  但是他不能承認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Will does, too, but he can't admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不能惹怒中堅選民  -對呀  中堅選民\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mustn't upset the base. - Ah, yes, the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能惹怒中堅選民\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mustn't upset the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.25,0:26:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實是我的榜樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know, you're actually a role model of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的那些工作  環保\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, your work on the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.27,0:26:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性侵犯  當大使...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}sexual assault, being ambassador...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  我更想我們贏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, obviously, I'd prefer if we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.45,0:26:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果贏不了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But if we didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.94,0:27:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能成為一名優秀的副總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think you'd make a wonderful Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.53,0:27:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  你在喝什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mommy, what are you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.69,0:27:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是咖啡  親愛的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's coffee, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.61,0:27:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要  我也想要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I want some! I want some!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.24,0:27:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這么大聲  會吵醒妹妹的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not so loud. You'll wake your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能喝一點嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can I have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.39,0:27:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還太小了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not old enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.11,0:27:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想喝水嗎  或是果汁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But do you want some water or some juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.78,0:27:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰箱里應該有果汁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think we've got some juice in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.14,0:27:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.06,0:27:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好可愛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.78,0:27:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你后悔沒要孩子嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you regret it, not having children?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.53,0:27:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  這個問題太私人了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'm sorry. That's too personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.95,0:27:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你后悔過要孩子嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you ever regret having them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.40,0:27:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音已經確認了  他們在線上  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've got voice verification. They're on the line, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.27,0:27:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要拖住他們好讓你們追蹤通話嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do I need to keep them engaged so you can trace the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  是網絡通話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, Internet call.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.20,0:27:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每30毫秒換路由  無法追蹤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Rerouted every three milliseconds. Untraceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.78,0:27:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有兩個主要目標\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have two main objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.12,0:27:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲取更多信息  拖延最后期限\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}More information, extending the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.43,0:27:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最重要的是證明人質還活著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But our top priority is a first concession. Proof of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.69,0:27:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你什么都別承諾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So you'll promise nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.95,0:28:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.69,0:28:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記住他們可能會對通話錄音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Keep in mind that they may be recording this call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.18,0:28:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想要炒作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's publicity they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.80,0:28:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我準備好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.20,0:28:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是康威州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is Governor Conway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.40,0:28:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和吉姆  卡洛琳和梅莉莎通話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to speak with Jim, Caroline and Melissa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.43,0:28:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要證據證明他們還活著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I need some proof that they're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.77,0:28:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴梅莉莎她的祖父母非常想念她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Please tell Melissa that her grandparents miss her very much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.47,0:28:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在為她祈禱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and, uh, they are praying for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這么做不會讓我們為他們感到抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna make us feel sorry for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向無辜的穆斯林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How sorry did you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.12,0:28:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投炸彈的時候  又有多抱歉  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}when you dropped bombs on innocent Muslims, Governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.79,0:28:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統是個懦夫  派別人去替他殺人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The President's a coward. He sends others to do his killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你更壞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But you're worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還發表講話說你對打了一場不義之戰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You make speeches about how proud you are
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到多么的自豪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that you fought in an unjust war.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.51,0:28:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果炸彈落在你女兒身上  你會是什么感受\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How would you feel if a bomb was dropped on your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.87,0:29:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她被炸飛  死無全尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If she was blown up and had to be buried in pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.55,0:29:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是美國人  對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're American, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.25,0:29:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們效忠于尤瑟夫·艾哈邁迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our allegiance is to Yusuf Al Ahmadi
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.44,0:29:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哈里發帝國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and the Islamic Caliphate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.29,0:29:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國是我們的敵人  必須滿足我們的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}America is our enemy and must meet our demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, you understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.17,0:29:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能代表政府說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't speak on behalf of the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.01,0:29:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能把你說的話轉達給總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can only communicate what you say to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要些時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll need some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我們傻嗎  他正聽著呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You think we're stupid? He's listening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.93,0:29:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is the President speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只和康威說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We talk to Conway only.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.88,0:29:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想要什么的話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But if you want anything to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.33,0:29:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我能辦到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm the one that can make it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.87,0:29:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什么什么都不做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then why have you done nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.99,0:29:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在和國會討論贖金的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm talking to Congress about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.53,0:29:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的軍事顧問討論撤軍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm consulting with my military advisers about a pullout,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.59,0:29:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這些都不可能在幾小時內完成\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but nothing can happen in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想拖延時間好找到我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You just want more time so you can find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.59,0:29:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在找你們嗎  是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are we looking for you? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.71,0:29:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為保證你們把米勒一家毫發無傷地交出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But that's only so you'll turn over the Millers without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.73,0:29:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有什么移交\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But there is no handing over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.99,0:29:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么滿足我們的要求  否則他們就得死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Either you give us what we want or we kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.06,0:30:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不證明他們還活著  我們什么都不會做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Nothing will happen until we have proof of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.99,0:30:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  給你個活著的證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right, here's your proof of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.29,0:30:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那女孩舌頭割了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Cut out the girl's tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.60,0:30:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -我是康威\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- No! - This is Conway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.17,0:30:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -請不要沖動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- No! - Please, before you do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.45,0:30:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-媽媽  -約書  扎克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mommy! - Josh. Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我們在乎你知道我們的身份嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you think we care you know who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.46,0:30:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  住手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.91,0:30:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你談談  一小會兒就行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to speak with you, just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.73,0:30:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話要說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I... I have something to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.88,0:30:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但別讓梅莉莎再叫了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I need Melissa to stop screaming
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.09,0:30:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-這樣我才能聽清你  -不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- so I can hear you. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能聽聽她說話嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can I hear her voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.39,0:30:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須聽見她說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.13,0:30:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這兒  我是梅莉莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm here. I'm Melissa.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.87,0:30:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  梅莉莎  我是威爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hi, Melissa. My name is Will--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.09,0:30:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽見她說話了  快說吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You heard her voice. Now talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.67,0:30:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.95,0:30:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我殺過很多人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, I... I've killed a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.59,0:30:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有無辜者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Some of them innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.19,0:31:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一晚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And every single night...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.32,0:31:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沒對我妻子說過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I haven't even told my wife this...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.29,0:31:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每一晚  我都做噩夢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but every single night, I have nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.61,0:31:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想象我自己的女兒  莉莉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I picture my own daughter, Lily,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.81,0:31:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妻子  兒子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and my wife... and my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.71,0:31:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你說的那樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}just like you described...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.25,0:31:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被炸飛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.04,0:31:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.23,0:31:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以說我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, you could say that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.68,0:31:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做噩夢是因為我做得不對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I have these demons because what I did was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.62,0:31:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你的動機是正義的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and that your cause is righteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.03,0:31:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我當時也認為我的動機是正義的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I believed that my cause was righteous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.58,0:31:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能撤銷發生的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And if I could take it all back...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.14,0:31:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會做同樣的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wouldn't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.84,0:31:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.49,0:31:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為我的行為感到羞恥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm ashamed of what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.44,0:31:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統說得對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, the president is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.23,0:32:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要更多時間來籌備你們的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need more time to work on your demands,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.85,0:32:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但更重要的是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.46,0:32:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你之前從沒殺過人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm guessing you've never killed anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.31,0:32:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為一個了解殺戮的人  我要說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And speaking as someone who knows what it means to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.41,0:32:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做出無法挽回之事前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you owe yourselves more time
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該給自己更多時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}before you do something you can never take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.01,0:32:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Josh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.33,0:32:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早九點  你們的最后期限\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}9:00 a.m. You have till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.45,0:32:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們結束通話了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They've ended the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.95,0:32:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得非常好  州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You did an excellent job, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.57,0:32:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.65,0:32:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有一通戰況室電話的錄音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have a recording of the Situation Room call
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.98,0:32:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由劫持者在不久前放出的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}released by the captors a short while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.64,0:32:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在播放音頻之前  我們想提醒聽眾們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Before playing this audio, we want to warn viewers
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.17,0:32:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中部分內容會令人不安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that there are sections that are very disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.41,0:32:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建議大家把電視靜音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You might want to mute the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.58,0:32:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都哪去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.56,0:32:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都去忙劫持的報導了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They all got pulled on the hostage story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.35,0:32:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他們叫回來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Get 'em back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.17,0:33:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有瑪姬·蒂爾頓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And Maggie Tilden, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.52,0:33:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉錄  馬上做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Transcribe this, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.69,0:33:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查塔努加市外方圓50英里范圍內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fifty mile radius outside of Chattanooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用偷來的信用卡買汽油\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Gas purchase on a stolen credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.42,0:33:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬斯特森的同學之一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}One of Masterson's classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.66,0:33:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在要放出他們的照片嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Should we just release their photographs at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.57,0:33:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的電話被打爆了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm getting bombarded with calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.85,0:33:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州長用的是名字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, the governor used the first names.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.88,0:33:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有人把線索拼湊起來的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Someone's gonna put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.96,0:33:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們不如利用這一點  -先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- We might as well exploit it. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.30,0:33:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喬治  -總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- George. - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.11,0:33:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常  我會給你時間重新考慮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Normally, I'd give you time to reconsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.96,0:33:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天時間太緊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but time is in short supply today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.75,0:33:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不能這么對黨派\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't. Not to my party.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.02,0:33:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黨會撐下去的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The party will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.87,0:33:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威也許不能  沒辦法  他撒謊了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Conway might not, but too bad. He lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.10,0:33:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我這么對他  我就撐不過去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I do this to him, I don't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.87,0:33:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會被鄙視\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm vilified.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.90,0:33:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給你看點東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wanna show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.86,0:33:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這是什么嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.44,0:34:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我做黨鞭時\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is your magnet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在投票記數板上的磁鐵名牌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}from the vote count board when I used to be whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.20,0:34:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾有很多次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There were so many times when
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.00,0:34:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在我希望你在的位置  喬治\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you weren't in the column I wanted you to be in, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.68,0:34:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都知道  我那時有幾十次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And we both know that I could've forced you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.30,0:34:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以逼你按照我的意愿投票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to vote the way I wanted you to dozens of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.64,0:34:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我從沒那么做過  我克制住了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I never did. I held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.35,0:34:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了保護你的名譽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To protect your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.12,0:34:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做黨鞭的好處之一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And one of the advantages of being whip
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.85,0:34:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是每個黨員\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}is that behind every single member,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.81,0:34:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每塊磁鐵名牌之后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}behind all of these magnets,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.34,0:34:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都至少有一件不光彩的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}was at least one dishonorable thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過你的事恰好比大多數人都更不光彩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yours just happens to be more dishonorable than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.64,0:34:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這次我要把你放在我那一欄里  喬治\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So I'm putting you in my column this time, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.44,0:34:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安告訴我你在這兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}LeAnn told me you were in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.08,0:34:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在寫你的聲明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm working on your statements,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.14,0:34:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為最壞的情況做準備\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}in case the worst happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.20,0:34:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是緊張  這個地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's tense, this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.32,0:34:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墻壁里都透著這氣息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can feel it in the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.47,0:35:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早些時候去散步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I went for a walk earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.55,0:35:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣里都彌漫著緊張\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.31,0:35:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們交談都輕聲低語\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}People were talking in whispers,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.55,0:35:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然完全沒有必要這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}even though there was no reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.42,0:35:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就兩眼盯著手機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Or their eyes are glued to their phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.40,0:35:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有孩子在外面玩耍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And there are no children out...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.71,0:35:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個都沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想稱之為恐怖是有原因的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I guess they call it terror for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.09,0:35:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比恐怖更糟  是恐懼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Worse than terror. Dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們因一場悲劇把自己束縛起來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}People girding themselves for a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能反過來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mmm, and it could go the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.77,0:35:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.24,0:35:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢娜在照看她的孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hannah is minding her children.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.39,0:35:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在照看她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm minding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.20,0:35:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她丈夫的表現真是出色  是吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Her husband really knocked it out of the ballpark, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.01,0:35:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他說的是真心的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you think anything he says is genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.19,0:35:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不重要  不是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.77,0:35:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起作用了就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.09,0:36:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾經說你覺得康威只會表面功夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You said once you thought he was all surface, Conway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.02,0:36:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  自戀狂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, a narcissist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.33,0:36:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果給他一灘水照照自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But give him a pool to reflect in...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.67,0:36:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要當心了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.79,0:36:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎么做  他清楚得很\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He knows exactly what to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.12,0:36:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非他弄巧成拙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Unless he overreaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.75,0:36:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就希望如此嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is that what you were hoping?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.72,0:36:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他把這事搞砸嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That he was gonna fuck it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他不會搞砸的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because he's not gonna fuck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.41,0:36:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他太聰明了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's too smart for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.42,0:36:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他升到空中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"There he soared,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.98,0:36:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從大本鐘和倫敦眼旁邊呼嘯而過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}zipping past Big Ben and the London Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.78,0:36:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又從白金漢宮和皮卡迪利廣場上方飛過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}over Buckingham Palace and Piccadilly Circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.02,0:36:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  他遠去了"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Look at him go."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.04,0:36:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上回來  查理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be right back, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.78,0:36:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守夜的氣氛特別陰沉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}... the vigil is especially somber,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.13,0:36:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但上午早些時候達成的延期\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but there remains a great deal of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.38,0:36:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是帶來了不少希望\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}after the deadline was extended earlier this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.61,0:36:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很多人將延期歸功于州長  -情況如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Many credit that extension to Governor... - What's the latest?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.53,0:36:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有進展  搜索范圍縮小了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Progress. They've narrowed the search zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.35,0:36:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通話中  可以聽見梅莉莎在尖叫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}During the call, Melissa could be heard screaming
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.65,0:36:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為馬斯特森讓霍松"割掉..."\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as Masterson orders Hawthorne to, quote, "Cut out..."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.39,0:36:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水槽左邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Left of the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.77,0:37:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}此時康威州長介入\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's when Governor Conway stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.45,0:37:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你也來一瓶嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'm sorry. You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.49,0:37:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.24,0:37:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們播放他說的部分內容\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're going to play some of what he said right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.14,0:37:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-因為你的肝嗎  -對  我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Is it your liver? - Yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.33,0:37:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-保持清醒  -我殺過很多人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Clear mind. - I've killed a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.84,0:37:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有無辜者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Some of them innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.37,0:37:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一晚...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And every--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.87,0:37:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么關掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, why'd you turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時就在旁邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定讓你很抓狂吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's gotta drive you crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這下要有多少正面報道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How much good press I'm getting out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.51,0:37:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么這么好笑  -沒什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What's funny? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.50,0:37:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧  我也想聽笑話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Come on, tell me. I want in on the joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.69,0:37:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為你能激怒我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You think you can get under my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.10,0:37:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們第一次見面時  我就激怒你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I got under your skin the first time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.73,0:37:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么時候  新年前夜嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When? New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.44,0:37:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得我那晚恭維了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I believe I complimented you that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.82,0:37:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你盡可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But you go ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.75,0:37:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了擺出更高的姿態\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you tell yourself what you have to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.30,0:37:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自欺欺人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}in order to stand a little taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.48,0:37:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真為你難過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.97,0:37:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.35,0:37:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能待這么點時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's all you're gonna get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.94,0:37:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在任的時間不會比沃克長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna last any longer than Walker did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.72,0:38:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最讓你難受的  是我會做個了不起的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And what kills you is that I'll make a great president.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.07,0:38:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正會被銘記的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The kind of president who'll actually be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.21,0:38:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是比死還讓你難受嗎  弗蘭克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And isn't that worse than dying, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.25,0:38:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被遺忘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Being forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.06,0:38:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真以為你會是個了不起的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You actually think you'd make a great president.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.96,0:38:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只是小試牛刀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Today was just a little taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.90,0:38:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統99%的工作是不為人知的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}99% of this job is in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.26,0:38:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天在陽光下閃耀了一會兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, you had your little moment in the sun today,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.00,0:38:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但當你要做無數個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but what are you gonna do
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.09,0:38:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠無人知曉  無人感激的決定時\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}when you have to make a thousand decisions that no one will
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.81,0:38:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么辦呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}ever hear about or appreciate?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.02,0:38:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你很擅長競選總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think you're excellent at running for the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.77,0:38:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不認為你真有能力做總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I don't think you're equipped to actually be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.99,0:38:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這么居高臨下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't be condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.42,0:38:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是紐約州長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm the Governor of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.90,0:38:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾巴尼  是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ooh, Albany, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.00,0:38:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個冒牌貨  威爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're a pretender, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.74,0:38:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而如果你贏了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And if you win,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.03,0:38:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就從冒牌貨成了騙子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you'll go from pretender to fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.65,0:39:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓孩子們睡覺了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm putting the kids to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.45,0:39:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不耽擱你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't let me keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.52,0:39:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也許你該送他們回家  -還不到時候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Maybe you should send them home. - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.31,0:39:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了沃勒克還有別的打算嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you have something else in mind besides Walleck?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.64,0:39:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  而且我需要你幫我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, and I'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.21,0:39:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  你看見他了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Charlie? Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.86,0:39:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.26,0:39:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  你看我找到了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mommy, look what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.07,0:39:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快瞧瞧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, look at those.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.97,0:39:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我  你不能玩這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Give those back. Those aren't yours to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我能留著嗎  -快還回去  查理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Can I keep them? - Oh, um, hand them over, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-查爾斯  -要不這樣吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Charles. - No, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.19,0:39:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是留著吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You should keep them,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.41,0:39:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你這一生就應該順心如意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because you should get everything you want in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.47,0:40:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Um, say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.80,0:40:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謝謝你  -應該謝謝你才是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Thank you. - No, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.82,0:40:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你來白宮看我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for coming to the White House to visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.85,0:40:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都休息吧  明早七點見\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We should get some rest. I'll see you at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.95,0:40:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我早就起了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'll be up way before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.81,0:40:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.63,0:40:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么幫你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You need my help how?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.85,0:40:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還有誰知道  -沒人了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Who else knows about this? - No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.22,0:40:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你盡快安排\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll need you to make arrangements as quietly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.64,0:40:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我去辦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right, I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.94,0:40:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到地址之后馬上告訴你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll let you know as soon as I have a location.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.42,0:40:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  回家睡幾個小時吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Good. Then go home and get a few hours of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.09,0:40:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚可睡不著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.20,0:40:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試吧  我們需要你明早精力充足\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You should try. We'll need you fresh in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.02,0:40:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聯系參聯會主席  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Get me the Chairman Joint Chiefs. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.21,0:41:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在線上了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's on the line, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.08,0:41:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想什么時候聯系白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When do you wanna reach out to the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.58,0:41:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  郵件我已經寫好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tomorrow. I've drafted the email.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你已經檢查過了嗎  -是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You looked this over? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.55,0:41:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法律上我們沒有問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're okay on the legal front.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.63,0:41:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們不該等人質危機結束嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But shouldn't we wait until this crisis is over first?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.51,0:41:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不  這是我們的絕佳機會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No. This is perfect timing for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.71,0:41:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆說得對  趁他不備  攻他不意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tom's right. Let's hit him while he's distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.45,0:41:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.69,0:41:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.37,0:41:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冰箱里實在是沒什么可做的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, you didn't have much to work with in your fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.12,0:41:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得去買點吃的了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You need to do some grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.87,0:41:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不常做飯  -看出來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I don't cook a lot. - Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.87,0:41:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要的話就回去照顧孩子吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you have to get back to your kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.45,0:41:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈莉16歲了  有需要的話她會打給我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Haley's 16. She'll call me if she needs anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.34,0:42:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們看新聞了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have they been watching the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.93,0:42:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了  他們嚇壞了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah... and they're freaked out by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰不怕呢  但是他們現在承受能力強多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, who isn't? But they've got thick skin by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.71,0:42:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比他們的同齡伙伴們鎮靜多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Handling it a lot better than some of their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.30,0:42:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有好多父母\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know a lot of parents aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.33,0:42:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天甚至都不打算讓孩子出門了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}even letting their kids out of the house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.71,0:42:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連學也不上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not even to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.98,0:42:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我的孩子還是會去的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My kids are gonna go, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.22,0:42:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓這些畜生毀了我們的生活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not gonna let these monsters rule over our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.03,0:42:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-多謝你過來  -客氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Thanks for coming over. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.21,0:42:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算躺床上也只會盯著天花板發呆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know I'd just be staring at the ceiling if I tried to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.46,0:42:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作太繁重了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, you have a lot on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般我會去參加個互助會什么的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, normally, I'd go to a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.99,0:42:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I... I just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.07,0:42:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是希望能有人照顧你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You just wanted someone to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.67,0:42:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能照顧別人也挺好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And it's nice to take care of someone.
